trans-unit.source: Represents a Windows progress bar control contained in a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusStrip"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en Windows pågår for kontroll i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.StatusStrip"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: ToolStripProgressBar is the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> optimized for hosting in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.
trans-unit.target: ToolStripProgressBar er <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>optimalisert for vert i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStrip> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: A subset of the hosted control's properties and events are exposed at the ToolStripProgressBar level, but the underlying <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> control is fully accessible through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.ProgressBar%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Et delsett av den vertsbaserte kontrollen egenskaper og hendelser vises på ToolStripProgressBar-nivå, men den underliggende <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>kontrollen er fullstendig tilgjengelig via den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.ProgressBar%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.ProgressBar%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: A ToolStripProgressBar control visually indicates the progress of a lengthy operation.
trans-unit.target: En ToolStripProgressBar kontroll angir visuelt fremdriften for tidkrevende operasjoner.

trans-unit.source: The ToolStripProgressBar control displays a bar that fills in from left to right with the system highlight color as an operation progresses.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen ToolStripProgressBar viser en stolpe fyller ut fra venstre mot høyre med systemet fremheve farge som en operasjon pågår.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The ToolStripProgressBar control can only be oriented horizontally.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For ToolStripProgressBar kontrollen kan bare være innrettet vannrett.

trans-unit.source: The ToolStripProgressBar control is typically used when an application performs tasks such as copying files or printing documents.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen ToolStripProgressBar brukes vanligvis når et program utfører oppgaver som kopiering av filer eller skrive ut dokumenter.

trans-unit.source: Users of an application might consider an application unresponsive if there is no visual cue.
trans-unit.target: Brukere med en applikasjon kan du vurdere å et program ikke svarer Hvis det er ingen visuell effekt.

trans-unit.source: Use the ToolStripProgressBar to notify the user that the application is performing a lengthy task and that the application is still responding.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av ToolStripProgressBar til å varsle brukeren om at programmet utfører en lang oppgaven, og at programmet fortsatt svarer.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> properties define the range of values to represent the progress of a task.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>egenskapene definerer verdiområdet til å vise fremdriften for en oppgave.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> property is typically set to a value of zero, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property is typically set to a value indicating the completion of a task.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>vanligvis settes til verdien null, og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>vanligvis settes til en verdi som angir en oppgave er fullført.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, to display the progress properly when copying a group of files, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property could be set to the total number of files to be copied.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel for å vise fremdriften riktig ved kopiering av en gruppe filer, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>egenskapen kan settes til det totale antallet filer som skal kopieres.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property represents the progress that the application has made toward completing the operation.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen representerer pågår programmet foretok med å fullføre operasjonen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Because the bar displayed in the control is a collection of blocks, the value displayed by the ToolStripProgressBar only approximates the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property's current value.
trans-unit.target: Fordi linjen vises i kontrollen er en samling av blokker, verdien som vises med ToolStripProgressBar bare etterligner den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>gjeldende egenskapsverdien.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Based on the size of the ToolStripProgressBar, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property determines when to display the next block.
trans-unit.target: Basert på størrelsen på ToolStripProgressBar, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen bestemmer når til å vise neste blokken.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: There are a number of ways to modify the value displayed by the ToolStripProgressBar other than changing the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property directly.
trans-unit.target: Det finnes flere måter å endre verdien som vises med ToolStripProgressBar enn endring av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen direkte.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property to specify a specific value to increment the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property by, and then call the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> method to increment the value.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>til å angi en bestemt verdi for å øke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>ved og kaller den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A>metode for å øke verdien.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: To vary the increment value, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A> method and specify a value by which to increment the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: For å variere inkrementell-verdi, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A>metoden og angi en verdi som skal økes den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A>

trans-unit.source: ToolStripProgressBar replaces the older <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar> control, which is nevertheless retained for backward compatibility.
trans-unit.target: ToolStripProgressBar erstatter den eldre <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>kontrollen likevel er beholdt for bakoverkompatibilitet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> property is set to 0, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property is set to 100, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property is set to 10.
trans-unit.target: Som standard i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>egenskapen settes til 0, i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>er satt til 100, og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>egenskapen er satt til 10.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>

trans-unit.source: Advances the current position of the progress bar by the specified amount.
trans-unit.target: Flytter gjeldende posisjon på fremdriften for datamengden angitt.

trans-unit.source: The Increment method enables you to increment the value of the progress bar by a specific amount.
trans-unit.target: Metoden intervallet kan du øke verdien på fremdrift for en bestemt avstand.

trans-unit.source: This method of incrementing the progress bar is similar to using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden for intervaller pågår for fungerer som den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>egenskapen med den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property specifies the current position of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>Egenskapen angir den gjeldende posisjonen for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: If, after calling the Increment method, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property is greater than the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property remains at the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis etter intervall-metoden i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen er større enn verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>egenskapen den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen blir værende i verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: If, after calling the Increment method with a negative value specified in the `value` parameter, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property is less than the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> property, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property remains at the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis etter å kalle metoden intervall med en negativ verdi som er angitt i den `value` parameteren den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen er mindre enn verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>egenskapen den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen blir værende i verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value representing the delay between each <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBarStyle"></xref> display update, in milliseconds.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir forsinkelsen mellom hver <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ProgressBarStyle"> </xref> Vis oppdateringen i millisekunder.

trans-unit.source: The MarqueeAnimationSpeed property gets or sets the delay of display update.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen MarqueeAnimationSpeed henter eller angir forsinkelsen av oppdateringen for visning.

trans-unit.source: Therefore, as you decrease the value of the MarqueeAnimationSpeed property, the speed of the animation increases.
trans-unit.target: Derfor som du reduserer verdien for egenskapen MarqueeAnimationSpeed, øker hastigheten for animasjonen.

trans-unit.source: An integer representing the delay, in milliseconds.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som representerer forsinkelsen i millisekunder.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the upper bound of the range that is defined for this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den øvre grensen for området som er definert for dette <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property specifies the upper limit of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir den øvre grensen for det <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the value of the Maximum property is changed, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar> control is redrawn to reflect the new range of the control.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for egenskapen maksimalt er endret, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>kontrollen er trukket tilbake for å gjenspeile det nye området kontrollens.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: When the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property is equal to the value of the Maximum property, the progress bar is completely filled.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>er lik verdien for egenskapen maksimalt, linjen pågår er fullstendig fylt.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use this property to specify a value that the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property must be set to (by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property or using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> methods) to indicate that an operation is complete.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne egenskapen til å angi en verdi som den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen må være satt til (ved å angi den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen eller bruker den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A>metoder) til å angi at en operasjon er fullført.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, you can set the value of the Maximum property to the total number of files in a file copy operation.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel ikke angi verdien for egenskapen maksimalt antall filer i kopiering av filer.

trans-unit.source: Each time a file is copied, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property can be increased by one until the total number of files is copied.
trans-unit.target: Hver gang en fil kopieres, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen økes med én før totalt antall filer overført.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: At that point, the progress bar would be completely filled.
trans-unit.target: På dette tidspunktet vil pågår for bli fullstendig fylt.

trans-unit.source: An integer representing the upper bound of the range.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som representerer den øvre grensen for området.

trans-unit.source: The default is 100.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er 100.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the lower bound of the range that is defined for this <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir den nedre grensen for området som er definert for dette <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: This property specifies the lower limit of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen angir nedre grense for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the value of the Minimum property is changed, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar> control is redrawn to reflect the new range of the control.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for egenskapen Minimum er endret, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>kontrollen er trukket tilbake for å gjenspeile det nye området kontrollens.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>

trans-unit.source: When the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property is equal to the value of the Minimum property, the progress bar is empty.
trans-unit.target: Når verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>er lik verdien for egenskapen Minimum, linjen pågår er tom.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: To change the value of the progress bar, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property with the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> method, use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A> method, or set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property directly.
trans-unit.target: For å endre verdien av feltet pågår, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>egenskapen med den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A>metoden, bruk den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A>metode, eller angi verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen direkte.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.PerformStep%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: An integer representing the lower bound of the range.
trans-unit.target: Et heltall som representerer den nedre grensen for området.

trans-unit.source: The default is 0.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er 0.

trans-unit.source: Advances the current position of the progress bar by the amount of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step*> property.
trans-unit.target: Flytter gjeldende posisjon for linjen pågår for datamengden du <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step*>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step*>

trans-unit.source: The PerformStep method increments the value of the progress bar by the amount specified by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden PerformStep øker verdien for pågår for datamengden angitt av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property to specify the amount that each completed task in an operation changes the value of the progress bar.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>til å angi hvor hver fullførte i en operasjon endringer verdien pågår-feltet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if you are copying a group of files, you might want to set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property to 1 and the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property to the total number of files to copy.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du kopiere en gruppe filer, du kan for eksempel ikke angi verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>egenskapen 1 og verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>egenskapen Totalt antall filer som skal kopieres.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: When each file is copied, you can call the PerformStep method to increment the progress bar by the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Når hver fil kopieres, kan du kalle metoden PerformStep for å øke pågår for med verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Step%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you want to have more flexible control of the value of the progress bar, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A> method or set the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property directly.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil har mer fleksibel kontroll over verdien av feltet pågår, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A>metoden eller angi verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen direkte.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Increment%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property specifies the current position of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>Egenskapen angir den gjeldende posisjonen for <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: If, after calling the PerformStep method, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property is greater than the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property remains at the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis etter PerformStep-metoden i <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen er større enn verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>egenskapen den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen blir værende i verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Maximum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: If, after calling the PerformStep method with a negative value specified in the `value` parameter, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property is less than the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> property, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> property remains at the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Hvis etter å kalle metoden PerformStep med en negativ verdi som er angitt i den `value` parameteren den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen er mindre enn verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>egenskapen den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>egenskapen blir værende i verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Minimum%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar.Value%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"></xref> layout is right-to-left or left-to-right when the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"></xref> property is set to <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.ToolStripProgressBar"> </xref> oppsettet er høyre mot venstre eller venstre mot høyre når den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"> </xref> er satt til <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the RightToLeftLayout property to control the layout of international applications in which the language is written from right to left.
trans-unit.target: Bruk egenskapen RightToLeftLayout for å kontrollere oppsettet for internasjonale programmer språket skrives fra høyre mot venstre.

trans-unit.source: When the RightToLeftLayout property is `true`, and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft> property is set to <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft>, mirroring will be enabled on the Windows form and control placement and text will be from right to left.
trans-unit.target: Når egenskapen RightToLeftLayout er `true`, og <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft>er satt til <xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft>speiling aktiveres på Windows skjemaet og kontrollen plasseringen og teksten skal fra høyre mot venstre.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to turn on mirroring and lay out control from right to left when the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"></xref> property is set to <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>aktivere speiling og utforme kontrollen fra høyre mot venstre når den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"> </xref> er satt til <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.RightToLeft"> </xref>; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
